summary: recently rewatched a dan video after a year. i watched the living my truth video and then scrolled down to read the comments....
body:
recently rewatched a dan video after a year. i watched the living my truth video and then scrolled down to read the comments. and I think I know why dan isn’t posting anymore.


he talks about being depressed and honestly even though the video has some cringey humour he talks about something that you can tell he genuinely feels for. and then u go down to the comments and there’s all these people talking about oral fixation, this being the gayest video, him looking like a ‘daddy’ and just…,,,, i get it.


why the hell would anyone want to talk about anything they find relevant or anything they’re passionate about if they get this kind of reception from their audience? and in a way it’s a monster dans created. because you could argue that he didn’t need to put in those jokes to add fuel to the fire but i think he must feel like he NEEDS to cater to those fans to maintain relevancy. and even if he didn’t, people would find things anyway to oversexualise and completely miss the point.


all these people treat him like an object of their own little fantasies while completing forgetting he’s an actual real person even if they don’t want to admit it. they see videos like this and instead of thinking ‘oh he’s talking about something interesting i want to listen to him’ they immediately talk about how hot he looks in a fucking quiff or how hot he looks in phils glasses or whatever.


regardless, i don’t wanna say that i know for sure this is what’s happening but i just had some thoughts. i don’t think his fan base will ever be mature enough to enjoy the content he wants to make despite the fact that they think they are. mostly because they’re so consumed by the idea of his sexuality and his dynamic with phil.


if you don’t believe me, then you should think back to a year ago when this video did come out and i got an ask saying ‘oh yeah dan has another existential crisis what’s new about that we should be talking about his ORAL FIXATION’.


like, okay.

body:
here’s a couple of dan’s pictures:

here, dan is in his ii merch, which is amazing

here, a wild daniel howell can be spotted in his natural habitat, which includes an all-black aesthetic and ripped jeans


here, dan is in his famous black glitter jacket and earring

this picture represents one of the few times when dan rocked his fringe and successfully avoided a derpy picture.

novices and amateurs, take notes

now, onto some amazingphil pictures:

here’s a wild philly in good, ol’ germany. dan is nowhere to be found.

here’s phil from one of his many instagram stories.

here’s a phil lester picture with some classic philters

here’s a phil lester, who looks really similar to voldemort. however, like a wise man once said, one shall *ahem* bang *ahem* the dark lord. and the phandom shall comply.

agreed, this is a concept art/edit/manip(?), but they look really good with quiffs

DISCLAIMER: NO RATS AND VAMPIRES WERE HARMED IN THE PRODUCTION OF THESE WORKS OF ARTS.

Just got toasted.

Setting: Bingsu place

Time: approximately five minutes ago

Characters: me, sister, dad

*dad pays for strawberry bingsu*

Me: but dad! I want a mango bingsu!

Dad: but your sister hates mangoes and we all agreed to share one bowl!

*five minutes of sister and I fighting for food superiority*

Me: now i want an ube bingsu

Sister: NO.

Me: YOU HATE UBE?!!?

*another five minutes of fighting later*

Me: okay, how about this, since you DONT MIND eating strawberry bingsu, miss STRAWBERRY, why dont YOU eat the strawberry bingsu while Dan and I-

Sister: WHAT WAS THAT!?

Me: *realizes her mistake*

Me: crap.

Me: Dad you heard nothing! Just give me the strawberry bingsu!
